## âœ… **Takeaway**

| Concept       | Finite Automata | Pushdown Automata                      |         |          |
| ------------- | --------------- | -------------------------------------- | ------- | -------- |
| Memory        | No memory       | Has a stack (infinite memory in depth) |         |          |
| Language Type | Regular         | Context-Free                           |         |          |
| Example       | `{ aâ¿bâ¿         | nâ‰¥0 }` âŒ                               | `{ aâ¿bâ¿ | nâ‰¥0 }` âœ… |

