## **ğŸ’¡ Summary Table (Easy Format)**

| Transition           | Reads Input  | Stack Action          | Description                     |
| -------------------- | ------------ | --------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| Î´(p, a, Zâ‚€) = (q, Î³) | Reads `a`    | Replace `Zâ‚€` with `Î³` | Normal transition               |
| Î´(p, Îµ, Zâ‚€) = (q, Î³) | No input (Îµ) | Replace `Zâ‚€` with `Î³` | Epsilon move                    |
